<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_354_r1l23"><expan>Sweıck<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_354_r1l24"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> / Als Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough"> ew </del> vormals durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen gemüwet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_354_r1l25"><expan>geweſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeit in <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> ſache als Hılpolt <expan>Frawmberg<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒü Prunne </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_354_r1l26"><expan>etlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etwiuil habe <expan>aufgehalt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat / des wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_354_r1l27"><expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit cʒemals <expan>fleiʒʒikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>danke<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> etc <expan cert="medium">ger<ex>iht</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_354_r1l28"><expan>word<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ıſt / dabey Jr auch <expan>geweſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeit / . Nu <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr ew </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_354_r1l29"><expan>d<ex>ur</ex>ch</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> müwen / cʒü <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tage kümen vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_354_line_1576485504459_3668">
<del rend="strikethrough">do bey </del> darauf beÿ den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſein wöllet 
<add>
<del rend="strikethrough"><ab facs="#facs_354_line_1576485492597_3660">vnd <expan>dary<ex>nne</ex></expan> </ab></del></add>
<add><ab facs="#facs_354_line_1576485552508_3710">vnd ew <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_354_line_1576485554499_3715">beweıſen </ab></add> Als wir ein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_354_r1l32"><expan>beſund<ex>er</ex></expan> getrawen cʒü ew <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd das auch <expan>v<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>k<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_354_r1l34">cʒü allen <expan>cʒeit<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit wıllen <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dıene<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>vts<ex>upra</ex></expan> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_354" id="176v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Sweick<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, als ir vormals durch
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen gemüwet
                            <expan>gewese<ex>n</ex></expan> seit in <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        sache, als Hilpolt <expan>Frawmberg<ex>er</ex></expan> czü Prunne
                                <expan>etlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        etwivil habe <expan>aufgehalt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat, des wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit czemals
                                <expan>fleizzikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>danke<ex>n</ex></expan>, und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> etc.
                            <expan cert="medium">ger<ex>iht</ex></expan>
<expan>word<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ist, dabey ir auch
                            <expan>gewese<ex>n</ex></expan> seit. Nu
                        <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir ew <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>ch</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> müwen, czü <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        tage kümen und darauf bey den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sein wöllet
                            <add>und ew <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan> beweisen</add>, als wir ein
                                <expan>besund<ex>er</ex></expan> getrawen czü ew
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und das auch
                            <expan>u<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erb<ex>er</ex>k<ex>eit</ex></expan> czü allen
                            <expan>czeit<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit willen <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>diene<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>ut s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
